### Public list of posts
GET http://localhost:3000/posts

### Public single post
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Create a post (requires JWT or API key auth)
POST http://localhost:3000/posts
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hello Shaperail",
  "slug": "hello-shaperail",
  "body": "This post was created from the blog-api example.",
  "status": "published",
  "created_by": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "published_at": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z"
}

### List comments for a post
GET http://localhost:3000/comments?filter[post_id]=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Create a comment (requires JWT or API key auth)
POST http://localhost:3000/comments
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "post_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "body": "Great article.",
  "author_name": "Mahin",
  "created_by": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
}
